                < >**Manage Your Bankroll Wisely:** Set a realistic budget before you start playing and stick to it. Only wager what you can afford to lose, and avoid chasing losses.</ >
                < >**Progressive Betting Systems (Use with Caution):** These involve increasing or decreasing your bets based on the outcome of previous spins. Systems like Martingale or Fibonacci are popular, but remember, they don't guarantee wins and can lead to significant losses if used recklessly. Use them with caution and always prioritize responsible gambling practices.</ >
                </p>

            <p>**Important Note:** Progressive betting systems can be risky and are not recommended for beginners. They can lead to quickly exceeding your bankroll if you experience a losing streak.</p>

